parameters: Did we manage to make it somehow?

So this was a defense layer. I never expected
there to be something like this in the student
council room.
Someone's here. Let's hide for now.

Why would Hiyo do something like this... What
should we do, Amelia?

Because if I'm shown something like this, I'll get
horny... I can't calm down until I come once.
B-But in a place like this...

(There's no way Amelia would say something like
this...)

Hiyo-chan and the others were having sex too, so
it's not a big deal, right?

Please... If it's the two of us, it won't be
embarrassing.

Liar... Masamune-kun, you're also getting an
erection, aren't you?

Let's do it together... If you don't want to, then
watch me masturbate.
You can do it if you want.
Ah, how was my sex? It was amazing, right?
H-Hiyo wouldn't say something like that.

(Red eyes... Just like I saw in the previous loop.
It must be...)
By the way, you guys managed to come this far.

If it's the defense layer, it might be better to
make it more secure, don't you think?

I knew it, you're not just an ordinary transfer
student at this academy.

Does your personality only change when you have
those red eyes?

(The words and actions are so different... And
considering the name Hiyo murmured at that time...
It's only natural to think that way.)

Ah, that's right. You noticed even though it's
only been a few days since I transferred.

I wasn't really hiding it. Koyoko's personality
comes out on its own at night.

I generally stay quiet in my room, so it's not
widely known, but there are people who are aware.

(I've heard about it, but this is my first time
seeing it)
But... why did you do something like that?

That's just a hobby. I enjoy things that feel
good.
Like I would know about that.

But you noticed well. As a thank you, should I let
you fuck me once?

You just want to have sex, don't you? But... um, I
can't because there's someone I like.

I mean, I wouldn't do something like that with
someone I just met.

That young lady over there was looking eager to do
it. Will you do it instead?
No way! That topic is already over.
Well, never mind. Let's leave the jokes at that.

You went through the trouble of breaking through
the defense layers to infiltrate, so you must have
had a reason, right?

(I guess it's okay to say... You helped me last
time too)

(Since they already found out that I infiltrated,
it's impossible to hide it completely anyway)

Our objective is the summoning ritual magic
circle. We heard rumors that demon summoning was
taking place within the academy, so we
infiltrated.

They said it wasn't in the Magic Research Club,
but I still believe it exists within the academy.

And so, I came to investigate because I thought
the Student Council might be suspicious.

The magic circle is in the Student Council... It's
definitely strange to have only magical tools
without a magic circle.
So, which organization do you all belong to?

But I only came to stop the summoning of demons.
Once it's done, I'll leave the academy
immediately.

Well, whatever. Whether there's a spy infiltrating
the academy or not, it doesn't concern me.
So, what about the magic circle...

When I... no, when Hiyo went to see it, it really
wasn't there.

If you doubt it, feel free to investigate. It's
not in the student council room.

However, it is a fact that there was a magical
tool related to the magic circle.

I was actually trying to investigate that matter
myself.
Is that as the student council?

(As I thought, she said she was investigating the
Magic Research Club on her own in the previous
loop.)

(Hiyo still has secrets. But even if I ask now,
she probably won't tell me.)
If that's the case, would you like to cooperate?
Our goals are the same, so it should be fine.

(I've been well aware from the previous loops that
there are limits to what we can accomplish on our
own.)

(If Hiyo, who was able to handle the executives of
the Magic Research Club alone, becomes our ally,
it will greatly increase our fighting power.)
But we just met... I still don't know you well.
Somehow... I feel like it'll be okay.
You're the type who acts on intuition, huh?

Normally, I wouldn't cooperate with someone whose
true identity I don't even know, but for some
reason, I feel like it'll be okay.

As for me, I also want to prevent the summoning of
demons.

If our goals are the same, there shouldn't be any
problem with cooperating.
Well... I don't completely trust you, though.

Well then, let's stop here for today. I'm tired
too.
What, so you wanted it too after all?
Yeah. Well then, nice to meet you from now on.
